      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's not just a \"setback\" though. it's everything. i spent years building this, my entire identity is tied to it. now i'm just a guy who failed a bunch of people and lost their money. i can't even imagine face to face with my parents or my wife right now. everything i worked for is just a pile of debt. it feels like there's no version of the future where i'm not walking around with this massive weight of failure on me. it's like the light just went out.",
