      "content": "it just feels like putting a bandaid on a gunshot wound. people say \"rebuild,\" but how do you rebuild when you can't even look in the mirror? the debt isn't a problem to solve, it's a permanent label. i feel like a ghost already. i'm just looking for a way for the noise to stop, for the shame to just... end. it feels like the only way to actually solve the problem of me being a failure is to not be here to deal with it anymore.",
